quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"We sent Thamud their brother Salih: [who said]: \"Worship God [Alone]!\" Nonetheless they became two quarreling factions"
  27,46,"He said: \"My people, why do you hasten towards evil rather than something fine? If you only sought forgiveness from God, you might find some mercy"
  27,47,"They said: \"Shall we take it as an omen from you and from someone who is with you?\" He said; \"Your fate depends on God; in fact, you are a folk who will be tested"
  27,48,There was a gang of nine persons in the city who caused trouble on earth and never improved matters
  27,49,"They said: \"Let´s all swear by God that we shall catch him and his family some night. Then we shall tell his next of kin: ´We did not witness the slaughter of his family. We are telling the truth!\"´"
  27,50,"They plotted away while We plotted too, and they did not even notice it"
  27,51,See what was the outcome of their plotting! We annihilated them and their folk completely
  27,52,"Those used to be their houses - [now] empty because of the wrong they had committed! In that is a sign for folk who know"
  27,53,We saved the ones who believed and had been doing their duty
  27,54,"When Lot told his folk: ´Do you indulge in sexual misconduct with your eyes open"
  27,55,Do you approach men passionately instead of women? Indeed you are folk who act out of ignorance